# Kite AA Contract Addresses (Testnet — DO NOT CHANGE)
# Settlement Token:      0x0fF5393387ad2f9f691FD6Fd28e07E3969e27e63
# Settlement Contract:   0x8d9FaD78d5Ce247aA01C140798B9558fd64a63E3
